Solution to:
https://github.com/votizen/careers/blob/master/RemoteCodingProblem.rst

Features:
- Requirements file for pip install
- Pagination for all list items (blog articles on homepage, and comments on post)
- Caching setup (uses redis) - both template fragment (for logged in users), and full view level for anonymous
- Twitter bootstrap for theming
- Gzip everything
- Unify css and js to reduce http requests, also minify
- WYSIWYG editing with TinyMCE